data.description: Great looking, professionally managed, single level rental home. It features brick & siding exterior, one car garage, 2 living areas, tile & hardwood floors, central heat & air and low-E windows. Home can be purchased individually or within package. See MLS 23033302 or MLS 23039446. Well maintained with records, selling as is where is. Agents see remarks.
